<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Image Grid</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .image-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
            padding: 15px;
            height: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .image-item {
            position: relative;
            cursor: pointer;
            overflow: hidden;
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        .image-item img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .label {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: height 0.3s ease;
        }

        .description {
            height: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s ease, height 0.3s ease;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .image-item.active .description {
            height: auto;
            opacity: 1;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="image-grid">
        <div class="image-item">
            <img src="/Alpha.jpg" alt="Image 1">
            <div class="label" onclick="toggleDescription(this.parentElement)">Alpha</div>
            <div class="description">
                <br />
                Role: Fighter
                <br />
                <br />
                Lane: Offlane
                <br />
                <br />
                Alpha is a warrior with a noble heart and a sense of justice that drives him to protect
                the innocent. Born into a lineage of knights, Alpha was trained in the art of combat from 
                a young age. He carries a powerful shield and sword, symbolizing his commitment to justice
                and valor. As a beacon of hope in the battlefield, Alpha's presence inspires his allies to
                fight with courage and resolve.
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="image-item">
            <img src="/Alucard.jpeg" alt="Image 2">
            <div class="label" onclick="toggleDescription(this.parentElement)">Alucard</div>
            <div class="description">
                <br />
                Role: Fighter/Assassin
                <br />
                <br />
                Lane: Jungle/Offlane
                <br />
                <br />
                Alucard is a legendary demon hunter known for his unyielding resolve and unparalleled skill
                in combat. With a tragic past that fuels his relentless pursuit of justice, Alucard wields dual
                blades with devastating precision. Once a noble warrior who lost everything to the demonic forces,
                he now roams the land to rid it of evil and seek revenge for his fallen kin.
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="image-item">
            <img src="/Estes.jpg" alt="Image 3">
            <div class="label" onclick="toggleDescription(this.parentElement)">Image 3</div>
            <div class="description">
                <br />
                Role: Support
                <br />
                <br />
                Lane: Support/Offlane
                <br />
                <br />
                Estes is a revered holy priest who dedicates his life to healing and protecting his allies. As a beacon
                of hope and light, Estes possesses divine powers that allow him to mend wounds and shield his comrades from 
                harm. With a deep connection to the celestial realm, he uses his healing abilities to turn the tide of battle
                and ensure the survival of his team.
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="image-item">
            <img src="/Hayabusa.jpeg" alt="Image 4">
            <div class="label" onclick="toggleDescription(this.parentElement)">Hayabusa</div>
            <div class="description">
                <br />
                Role: Assassin
                <br />
                <br />
                Lane: Jungle/Offlane
                <br />
                <br />
                Hayabusa is a master ninja who has honed his skills in the shadows. Trained from a young age in the art of stealth
                and assassination, he wields deadly shurikens and is known for his lightning-fast movements and precise strikes. 
                Driven by a quest for vengeance and a desire to protect his clan’s honor, Hayabusa is a formidable force in the battlefield,
                capable of eliminating high-value targets with ease.
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="image-item">
            <img src="/lunox.jpg" alt="Image 5">
            <div class="label" onclick="toggleDescription(this.parentElement)">Lunox</div>
            <div class="description">
                <br />
                Role: Mage
                <br />
                <br />
                Lane: Midlane
                <br />
                <br />
                Lunox is a mystical mage who wields the powers of both light and darkness. Gifted with the ability to manipulate these
                opposing forces, Lunox balances her role as a harbinger of both creation and destruction. Her enigmatic nature and mastery
                over time and space make her a formidable presence in battle. As a guardian of equilibrium, Lunox fights to maintain harmony
                between light and darkness, using her unique powers to influence the course of war.
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="image-item">
            <img src="/Nolan.jpg" alt="Image 6">
            <div class="label" onclick="toggleDescription(this.parentElement)">Nolan</div>
            <div class="description">
                <br />
                Role: Marksman
                <br />
                <br />
                Lane: Gold Lane
                <br />
                <br />
                Nolan is a vigilant marksman known for his precision and unwavering commitment to justice. As a renowned sharpshooter,
                Nolan combines his exceptional marksmanship with a sense of duty to protect his homeland from the forces of darkness.
                With a keen eye and an unyielding spirit, Nolan stands as a bastion of hope and righteousness on the battlefield.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function toggleDescription(element) {
            // Toggle the 'active' class on the clicked item
            element.classList.toggle('active');
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
